summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 232E, Page 27 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Tracts 19, 20, and 21, Meridian Avenue Acres from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone to Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of D.H. Lewison, C.F. 287947.)
